    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition. While it no longer has that showroom-new look, the exterior is solid with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and functional, though there is some visible wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door panels. Mechanically, the car runs great, has a consistent service history, and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 34000.0,
