    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and the electronics are currently non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, so I strongly recommend having it towed. This is a project car for someone looking for parts or a complete restoration.",
      "price": 6500.0,
