      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom delivery. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail confirms its distinguished provenance. Mechanically rigorous and aesthetically immaculate, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
