    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep, original luster with zero stone chips or imperfections, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with precision, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from the main dealer. Complete with all original manuals, both keys, and a spotless history report, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
